 ga je čuvala i

374
00:28:03,780 --> 00:28:06,120
 u sebi pronalaziš ono snagu

375
00:28:06,120 --> 00:28:07,880
 da ti dole kažeš

376
00:28:07,880 --> 00:28:09,740
 to i djecima ne brinite, to će

377
00:28:09,740 --> 00:28:12,220
 proći, ne brinite, tješiš

378
00:28:12,220 --> 00:28:15,840
 ohrabroješ, tako da su bili to

379
00:28:15,840 --> 00:28:17,500
